  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >History</h2>There's a story about a legendary treasure hidden on an unknown island. This treasure is so grand that it can turn a simple pirate into the king of pirates. However, the map leading to the island was divided into four parts, and their locations remain unknown.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532590/extras/0134a3700bec51329ca2e0fa471d4d56.poster.avif?t=1728840621\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532590/extras/0134a3700bec51329ca2e0fa471d4d56.webm?t=1728840621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532590/extras/0134a3700bec51329ca2e0fa471d4d56.mp4?t=1728840621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>When all four parts of the map are gathered, the group will set sail towards the treasure island<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532590/extras/a4a7311471f9032525b7af110c9dc86d.poster.avif?t=1728840621\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532590/extras/a4a7311471f9032525b7af110c9dc86d.webm?t=1728840621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2532590/extras/a4a7311471f9032525b7af110c9dc86d.mp4?t=1728840621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Credits</h2><br><strong>Art</strong><br>Pixel Frog<br>Anokolisa<br>BlackSpire Studio<br>Bayat Games<br>Greenpixels<br><br><strong>music</strong><br>Alkakrab<br>Leohpaz",
